data.description: **BUYER LOSS IS YOUR GAIN** SELLER IS READY TO MOVE! Beautiful home in NE San Antonio!  Inviting entry welcomes you to the gracious living/dining area combined with the island kitchen.  This cooks kitchen features 42in cabinets, lots of countertop space, nice appliances and large island all while a enjoying the open living room.  All tile throughout!  Master is oversized with private bathroom featuring walk-in shower, dual storage closets and large walk-in closet.  Interior laundry room has space for a 2nd fridge or freezer.  Garage offers wire shelving & water softener.  No neighbor directly behind, backyard with covered back patio, extended patio section and shed.
